casebody.data:
De Ruyter, Respondent, v. Manhattan Ry. Co., Appellant. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. March 3, 1891.) Appeal from judgment on report of referee.

Argued before Daly, C. J., and Bischoff. and Pryor, JJ.

Davies & Rapallo, for appellant. I. A. Weekes, Jr., for respondent.

No opinion. • Judgment affirmed, with costs.
